              <svg className="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2.5" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
            </button>
            <h2 className="text-xl md:text-3xl font-black text-cyan-400 mb-6 md:mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-4 md:pl-6">Operasi Sistem</h2>
            <div className="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-xs md:text-base text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium">
              <div className="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 items-start">
                <div className="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center font-black flex-shrink-0 border border-cyan-500/20 shadow-inner text-[10px] md:text-sm">01</div>
                <p>Konfigurasi <b>Target Rata-rata</b> akhir dan <b>Total Semester</b> yang akan ditempuh.</p>
              </div>
              <div className="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 items-start">
                <div className="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center font-black flex-shrink-0 border border-cyan-500/20 shadow-inner text-[10px] md:text-sm">02</div>
                <p>Pada <b>Semester 1</b>, definisikan seluruh mata pelajaran. Daftar ini akan disinkronkan otomatis.</p>
              </div>
              <div className="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 items-start">
                <div className="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center font-black flex-shrink-0 border border-cyan-500/20 shadow-inner text-[10px] md:text-sm">03</div>
                <p>Input nilai pada setiap semester yang telah selesai.</p>
              </div>
              <div className="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 items-start">
                <div className="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center font-black flex-shrink-0 border border-cyan-500/20 shadow-inner text-[10px] md:text-sm">04</div>
                <p>Gunakan tombol <b>"Analisis Hasil"</b> untuk mendapatkan proyeksi nilai minimal sisa semester.</p>
