            <a href="https://dapidhub.my.id" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" className="px-8 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-500 hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-slate-950 transition-all font-black uppercase text-[9px] tracking-widest">Developer Network</a>
